## Conventions

- **Component/Directive prefix**: `{{PREFIX}}` (update as the project grows).
- **Styling**: SCSS — but **every visual value comes from the design system** (`packages/design-system`), never from the component. Summon it with `@use 'design-system/styles' as ds;` and read tokens (`ds.color('on-surface')`, `ds.space(3)`); a component's own SCSS should be little more than layout. See `HOUSE.md` → **Design-system-first**.
- **Layout**: apps in `apps/`, libraries in `libs/`, publishable libraries (incl. the design system) in `packages/`; one Nx project each.
